ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: Visit name
Notes: e.g., Baseline, 6-Month Follow Up, Year 2

ElementDescription: The problems of taking care of a child are easy to solve once you know how your actions affect your child, an understanding I have acquired.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Even though being a parent could be rewarding, I am frustrated now while my child is at his / her present age.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I go to bed the same way I wake up in the morning, feeling I have not accomplished a whole lot.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I do not know why it is, but sometimes when I'm supposed to be in control, I feel more like the one being manipulated.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: My mother/father was better prepared to be a good mother/father than I am.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I would make a fine model for a new mother/father to follow in order to learn what she/he would need to know in order to be a good parent.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Being a parent is manageable, and any problems are easily solved.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: A difficult problem in being a parent is not knowing whether you're doing a good job or a bad one.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Sometimes I feel like I'm not getting anything done.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I meet by own personal expectations for expertise in caring for my child.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: If anyone can find the answer to what is troubling my child, I am the one.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: My talents and interests are in other areas, not being a parent.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Considering how long I've been a mother, I feel thoroughly familiar with this role.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: If being a mother/father of a child were only more interesting, I would be motivated to do a better job as a parent.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I honestly believe I have all the skills necessary to be a good mother/father to my child.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Being a parent makes me tense and anxious.
Notes: 6= Strongly Disagree; 5= Somewhat Disagree; 4= Disagree; 3= Agree; 2= Somewhat Agree; 1= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Being a good mother is a reward in itself.
Notes: 1= Strongly Disagree; 2= Somewhat Disagree; 3= Disagree; 4= Agree; 5= Somewhat Agree; 6= Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Timepoint/visit label
Notes: e.g., Baseline, Morning, At Bedtime
